Package: apigpt
Title: apigpt adds functionality based on OpenAI's GPT family of models directly into Rstudio
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Paul Efren", "Santos Andrade", , "paulefrens@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: OpenAI offers a number of large language models (LLMs) accessible via API. This package lowers the barrier to using this API inside of RStudio IDE.
